They are fiIghting--fiIghting for freedom.

1643
02:08:16,720 --> 02:08:18,710
自由?  胡扯
Freedom? Bullshit.

1644
02:08:18,920 --> 02:08:21,820
法国人胡话  美国人胡话
French bullshit. American bullshit.

1645
02:08:22,120 --> 02:08:24,460
奠边府的陷阱
Dien Bien Phu, that serious.

1646
02:08:24,630 --> 02:08:28,360
所有士兵  都知道他们已经完了
All soldiers know they are already dead.

1647
02:08:29,870 --> 02:08:31,700
你知道奠边府战役吗?
You know anything about Dien Bien Phu?

1648
02:08:34,900 --> 02:08:36,600
-我知道  -不  你不知道
-Yeah, I know.  -No, you don't.

1649
02:08:37,840 --> 02:08:38,810
不真的知道
Not really.

1650
02:08:39,010 --> 02:08:42,000
奠边府是个错误  一个军事错误
Dien Bien Phu was an error.A military mistake.

1651
02:08:42,210 --> 02:08:44,480
错误?  是个故意的错误!
A mistake? A voluntary mistake!

1652
02:08:44,680 --> 02:08:46,380
故意的!
Voluntary!

1653
02:08:48,320 --> 02:08:50,580
所有士兵都知道
All the soldiers knew.

1654
02:08:50,820 --> 02:08:52,520
我们知道自己会死
We knew we would be dead.

1655
02:08:52,520 --> 02:08:54,220
那些将军和上校以为
The generals and the colonels believe it's impossible for the Viets...

1656
02:08:54,360 --> 02:08:58,120
