When it comes, no airplane can fly there.

1660
02:09:08,420 --> 02:09:11,220
我们的伞兵  从90米高往下跳下
And our paratroopers jump at 90 meters.

1661
02:09:11,260 --> 02:09:13,720
90米  70米
I mean, you know, 90 meters--70 meters.

1662
02:09:13,930 --> 02:09:15,560
真是发疯
I mean, that's crazy.

1663
02:09:15,560 --> 02:09:17,190
没哪支军队会那样干
No army in the world can do that.

1664
02:09:17,800 --> 02:09:21,230
他们只想跟朋友们死在一起
And they only do that to be dead with their friends.

1665
02:09:27,540 --> 02:09:29,770
法国军队被牺牲了
The French Army was sacrifiIced.

1666
02:09:29,980 --> 02:09:32,540
被安安稳稳在家的政客们牺牲了
SacrifiIced by the politicians safe at home.

1667
02:09:32,750 --> 02:09:33,600
他们把军队推入了
They put the army in an impossible situation

1668
02:09:34,310 --> 02:09:35,870
不可能取胜的境地
where they couldn't win.

1669
02:09:36,720 --> 02:09:40,050
学生们在巴黎游行示威
The students are marching in Paris protesting, demonstrating.

1670
02:09:40,250 --> 02:09:42,280
从背后捅了士兵们一刀
They stab the soldiers in their back.

1671
