The soldier would open the grenade,

1672
02:09:45,020 --> 02:09:46,320
它却不会爆炸
it wouldn't work.

1673
02:09:46,530 --> 02:09:48,720
一张字条掉了出来
A piece of paper would fall--

1674
02:09:50,800 --> 02:09:53,990
法国妇女联盟  我们支持越南
''Union of French Women.'' ''We are for the Viets.''

1675
02:09:54,300 --> 02:09:58,630
叛徒! 国内的共产党叛徒
Traitors! Communist traitors at home.

1676
02:09:59,670 --> 02:10:02,200
这就是奠边府
Dien Bien Phu, okay.

1677
02:10:02,840 --> 02:10:05,000
法国人是混蛋
The French is shit, huh?

1678
