you could win if you want to!

1683
02:10:21,810 --> 02:10:23,570
你们能赢
You can win.

1684
02:10:26,750 --> 02:10:30,080
我肯定我们能在这有所作为
You know, I'm sure we can make something here.

1685
02:10:30,250 --> 02:10:32,220
我肯定
I'm sure about it, you know?

1686
