Capitaine, good night.

1690
02:11:16,800 --> 02:11:18,000
他是个社会主义者
He was a Socialist, you know.

1691
02:11:18,000 --> 02:11:19,200
我知道我们能留下
I know that we can stay.

1692
02:11:19,400 --> 02:11:22,630
我知道我们能留下并开创事业
I know that we can stay.We can.

1693
02:11:26,110 --> 02:11:29,510
我们经常帮越南人
You know, we always helped the people.

1694
02:11:29,730 --> 02:11:31,290
跟他们一起干活
We work with the people.

1695
02:11:32,400 --> 02:11:35,860
所以我们  可以推断自己是受欢迎的
So we can be friends, we are agreed.

1696
02:11:47,930 --> 02:11:52,230
瞧  上尉  我的祖父
See, Captain, when my grandfather...

1697
02:11:53,500 --> 02:11:56,940
和叔父刚来时
and my uncle's father came here...

1698
02:11:58,410 --> 02:12:01,870
这里一片荒芜
there was nothing--nothing.

1699
02:12:02,340 --> 02:12:04,900
越南什么也不是
The Vietnamese were nothing.

1700
02:12:06,520 --> 02:12:10,180
于是我们非常努力地工作
So we worked hard...

1701
02:12:10,390 --> 02:12:13,080
从巴西运来橡胶树
the rubber from Brazil,

1702
