I will see if your men need any help

1713
02:13:02,970 --> 02:13:05,320
是否需要东西修船
to repair your boat...

1714
02:13:05,520 --> 02:13:09,320
好继续你们的战争
so that you can go on with your war.

1715
02:13:44,210 --> 02:13:47,240
我为我的家人向你道歉  上尉
I apologize for my family, Captain.

1716
02:13:48,820 --> 02:13:51,120
我们都在这里失去了很多
We have all lost much here.

1717
02:13:52,320 --> 02:13:56,020
赫伯特失去了妻子和两个孩子
Hubert--his wife and two sons.

1718
02:14:00,010 --> 02:14:02,710
