And I have lost a husband.

1719
02:14:07,890 --> 02:14:09,680
我明白了
I understand.

1720
02:14:09,890 --> 02:14:12,520
你厌倦了战争
You are tired of the war.

1721
02:14:14,090 --> 02:14:16,720
我能从你脸上看出来
I can see it in your face.

1722
02:14:18,700 --> 02:14:22,830
和法国士兵眼神里的一个样
'Twas the same in the eyes of the soldiers of our war.

1723
02:14:24,440 --> 02:14:27,500
我们称他们为
We called them ''Les Soldats Perdus--''

1724
02:14:28,270 --> 02:14:30,610
迷失的士兵
The Lost Soldiers.

1725
02:14:34,900 --> 02:14:37,870
如果你愿意  我们可以来点科纳克白兰地
If you like, we can have some cognac.

1726
02:14:42,200 --> 02:14:43,640
不了
No.I...

1727
02:14:44,740 --> 02:14:48,180
我得去找我的部下  而且
I have to--to see about my men and--

1728
