我注意到你晚餐时没喝酒
I noticed you had no wine at dinner.

1731
02:15:22,290 --> 02:15:25,890
我不喝酒
No, I don't drink wine.

1732
02:15:28,430 --> 02:15:30,960
我是喜欢科纳克
I do like cognac,

1733
