Will you go back after the war to America?

1737
02:15:57,180 --> 02:15:58,370
不会
No.

1738
02:15:58,580 --> 02:16:02,480
那你跟我们一样  家就在这
Then you're like us--your home is here.

1739
02:16:19,550 --> 02:16:21,700
你知道人为什么
Do you know why you can never step

1740
