我不晓得自己  是畜生还是神
''I don't know whether I'm an animal or a god.''

1750
02:17:18,330 --> 02:17:20,290
但你两者皆是
But you are both.

1751
02:18:02,050 --> 02:18:04,210
还要吗?
You want more?

1752
02:18:09,290 --> 02:18:13,200
重要的是  你还活着
All that matters is that you're alive.

1753
02:18:14,770 --> 02:18:17,630
