You are alive, Captain.

1754
02:18:21,040 --> 02:18:23,170
这就是真相
That's the truth.

1755
02:19:36,460 --> 02:19:40,090
你看不到有两个你吗?
There are two of you, don't you see?

1756
02:19:41,300 --> 02:19:46,470
一个杀人  一个爱人
One that kills...and one that loves.

1757
02:20:14,820 --> 02:20:17,720
什么也看不见  停下
Can't see nothing. We stoppin'.

1758
